mil.nga.giat.geowave.core.store.query

Interface DistributableQuery

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Persistable, Query
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BasicQuery, CoordinateRangeQuery, CQLQuery, IndexOnlySpatialQuery, SpatialQuery, SpatialTemporalQuery, TemporalQuery

    public interface DistributableQuery
extends Query, Persistable
    This interface fully describes a query and is persistable so that it can be distributed if necessary (particularly useful for using a query as mapreduce input)
